{"tid":1944692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麻生太郎:WHO 應叫「中國衛生組織」","createTime":"2020-03-26T14:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T01:22:26.000Z","uid":75656,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"663d3c984b8d8719c7d164c3f99e42f4064f48e0","tid":1944692,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本副首相兼財務大臣麻生太郎繼直言不相信中國通報的武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情數據後，今（26）日在參議院答詢時，稱世界衛生組織（WHO）應叫「中國衛生組織」。<br />\n<br />\n《共同社》報導，麻生太郎26日出席參院財政金融委員會會議時，有在野黨議員提到網路出現以WHO未能保持政治上中立為由，要求秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）辭職的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n對此，麻生表示，「出現大量聲音說（WHO）不是世界衛生組織，應該改成中國衛生組織」。<br />\n<br />\n麻生先前曾在記者會等場合把新型冠狀病毒稱為「武漢病毒」，本月19日在參院答詢時，針對中國宣稱18日湖北省武漢肺炎首次新增病例為零，他稱「我認為不相信才是正確的」。<br />\n<br />\n麻生當時直言，「相信（中國）這個國家發布的數字，大概基本上就錯了。所以我認為，不相信才是正確的。」針對疫情在中國已平息的說法，他更說，中國國家主席習近平「好像哇啦哇啦地（對此）說個不停」，但他總懷疑「最好是啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3114013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3114013&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e500beb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3114013&h=e914e822\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3114013</a><br />\n<br />\n共同社:<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/03/43cd944e11a7-who.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F43cd944e11a7-who.html&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=7a4cf85f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/03/43cd944e11a7-who.html</a>"},{"pid":"bd14a47d242798ef2290d192fdf96e56587277eb","tid":1944692,"uid":42820,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"架仔奧運延期左之後唔洗留力了"},{"pid":"ed3be1194d55f4fb1da803762ed17fed13453242","tid":1944692,"uid":5406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB